# The edge-ui-out/ directory is the //go:embed target for the
# Next.js static export. `make edge-ui` populates it from edge-ui/out
# after `next build`. We commit only the placeholder HTML the static-
# handler tests need + this .gitignore so `go test`/`go build` work on
# a fresh checkout without having run the make target — every other
# file is build output.
#
#   index.html      — TestStaticHandler_ServesIndexAtRoot
#   preview/_.html  — TestStaticHandler_SPAFallbackToPreviewPlaceholder
#                     (the /preview/<id> SPA-fallback placeholder)
*
!.gitignore
!index.html
!preview/
preview/*
!preview/_.html
